| Before (Callbacks) | After (Async/Await) |
|--------------------|---------------------|
| Nested callbacks | Flat, readable code |
| `callback(err)` | `throw err` or `reject(err)` |
| `callback(null, data)` | `return data` or `resolve(data)` |
| Manual error propagation | Try/catch blocks |

